Package registration

Class Course

java.lang.Object
registration.Course
public class Course extends Object
The Course class holds information about a course. For example, CPSC 5011: Object-Oriented Concepts - subject code: CPSC - course number: 5011 - course name: Object-Oriented Concepts - credit number: 3 - prerequisite(s): CPSC 5005 (can have multiple prerequisites or none)
